char *  name

This creates a page provider that provides a single page filled with a fixed int.

Parameters:
[in] value The value to fill the pages with.
[in] recordsPerPage The number of records to return with each page.
[in] name The name of the provider. Can contain any string, this may be a column name, an expression, etc.
